      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty assessment not required at MRL 2 Gradation 1. Turbulence model and hemolysis power-law model selection are documented but formal uncertainty quantification is not required.",
      "rationale": "Model form is not assessed at MRL 2. The SST k-omega turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model are selected based on published best-practice guidance for pump hemolysis CFD. Formal model form uncertainty quantification is deferred."
    },
