      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameter uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2 Gradation 1. Nominal input values must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Model inputs are not formally assessed at MRL 2. Blood viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s), density (1056 kg/m³), and power-law hemolysis coefficients are set to published nominal values. Sensitivity to input variation is not formally quantified at this risk level."
    },
